%N A189856 Number of ways to place n nonattacking composite pieces rook + rider[2,5] on an n X n chessboard.
%C A189856 a(n) is also number of permutations p of 1,2,...,n satisfying |p(i+2k)-p(i)|<>5k AND |p(j+5k)-p(j)|<>2k for all i>=1, j>=1, k>=1, i+2k<=n, j+5k<=n
